This is legacy version of *mbank-cli*, a command line interface to the
on-line banking system of mBank.

**Warning**: You use *mbank-cli* on your own risk! The software is provided
“as is”, without warranty of any kind.

**Warning**: This version of *mbank-cli* uses the web interface at
https://www.mbank.com.pl/, which is in the process of being shut down.

Requirements
------------

- Perl (≥ 5.10) with the following Perl modules:

  - HTML::Form

  - HTML::Entities

  - HTTP::Cookies

  - LWP::UserAgent

  - LWP::Protocol::https

  - IO::Socket::SSL

- GnuPG (optionally, to protect your password)

